      "parameters": {
        "content": "The Project: Automated Email Summarizer\n​This tool pulls new emails from a Gmail account, uses an AI model to extract key information and action items, and then organizes those summaries into a Google Sheet or sends them as a notification to Slack/Telegram.\n​Why this project works for your portfolio:\n​Demonstrable Value: It directly addresses \"email clutter,\" a universal business pain point.\n​Technical Breadth: It forces you to use a trigger (Gmail/Webhook), data processing (filtering/formatting), AI logic (LLM node), and output (Google Sheets/Slack/Telegram).\n​Highly Demonstrable: You can easily record a 60-second video demo showing how an email lands in your inbox and how the summary appears in your organized dashboard.",
