    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert email assistant. Summarize the email below and extract action items.\n\nEMAIL DATA:\nFrom: {{ $json.From }}\nSubject: {{ $json.Subject }}\nBody: {{ $json.snippet }}\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n- Write a concise 2-3 sentence summary of what the email is about.\n- List any action items / tasks the recipient needs to do, each as a short bullet.\n- Assign a priority: High, Medium, or Low, based on urgency and deadlines mentioned.\n- If a deadline or date is mentioned, capture it. If none, write \"None\".\n- Keep it factual. Do not invent details not present in the email.\n\nRespond in exactly this format:\n\nSender: <sender>\nSubject: <subject>\nSummary: <2-3 sentence summary>\nAction Items:\n- <item 1>\n- <item 2>\nDeadline: <deadline or \"None\">\nPriority: <High/Medium/Low>",
        "batching": {}
      },
